Step 1: Architecture Overview

Browser → Ingress → Frontend Service → Frontend Pod
                   ↓
                   Backend Service → Backend Pod → MongoDB Service → MongoDB Pod

Every services will be isolated

We will be building 3 microServices: 
1.Frontend
*Runs React build output
*Served using NGINX
*Talks to backend using http://backend-service:8000

2.Backend
*Python FastAPI 
*Handles API CALLS
*Reads DB config from ConfigMap and Secrets
*Connects to MongoDB through mongoDb-services

3.MongoDB
*Official Mongo image
*Persists data using PVC
